h: hi robot!
r: hello
#Act h: puts a red box in front of the robot
r: what is that
#Hypothesis: express uncertainity about sth
h: do you know what this is ?
r: no, I do not know what this is 
h: this is a box.
r: let me see 
r: is the box red
#Hypothesis: verify uncertainity of color. However,
# Default voice suggests the presence of something besides a box.
h: yes, it is red.
r: okay!
#Act h: puts a red ball in front of the robot
h: what is this?
r: this is a red ball
#Hypothesis: red is the background, ball is the focus in the set of alternatives, however
#Default voice always focuses on the color
h: right!
#Act h: puts a green box in front of the robot
h: do you know what this is ?
r: it is a green box
#Hypothesis: box is the background, color green is the focus in the set of alternatives
#Default voice always focuses on the color
h: that is right!
